Message: Hi, Iâ€™m the NewsBreak Ad Assistant. How can I help?
The user completes the submission of the form
Hello, my campaigns are not serving impressions. Can you assist?

Hi Reeba, I'd be happy to help you with your campaigns. Could you please provide more details about the issue? Are there any error messages or notifications you're seeing? Also, have you checked if your ads are approved and if your targeting settings are correctly configured?
No error messages. Campaign and creatives are active. But not serving any traffic

Thanks for the details, Reeba. Let's check a few things to troubleshoot this issue:
1. **Budget and Bidding**: Ensure that your daily budget and bid rates are set appropriately. Sometimes, low bids can result in fewer impressions.
2. **Targeting Settings**: Double-check your audience targeting settings to make sure they are not too narrow.
3. **Ad Schedule**: Verify that your ads are scheduled to run during the times you expect them to.
4. **Ad Approval**: Confirm that all your ads have been approved and are not under review.
For more detailed guidance, you can refer to our [Account Management Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17539290349709-Account-Management-Guide).
If everything seems correct and you're still facing issues, I recommend reaching out to our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com with details about your campaign settings for further assistance.
Great! If you need any further assistance or have any other questions, feel free to ask. I'm here to help!
can I connect with a rep?

I'm here to help with whatever you need! Let me know your question, and I'll do my best to assist you right away. If you still need to connect with a representative, I can help you get in touch with our support team.
yes, please connect me to your support team
I've connected you with our support team. They will reach out to you shortly to assist with your issue. If you need anything else in the meantime, feel free to ask!
You're welcome, Reeba! If you have any other questions or need further assistance, don't hesitate to reach out. Have a great day!
